DIGITAL PORTFOLIO

----------------------------------------

Introduction

A digital portfolio is an online collection of a student’s work, achievements, and professional information. It helps in building a strong digital identity and is useful for internships, jobs, and networking opportunities. In this task, I created and updated my profiles on GitHub and LinkedIn.

----------------------------------------

GitHub Profile

GitHub is a platform used by developers to store, manage, and share their coding projects. It is widely used for collaboration and version control.

I created my GitHub account and added the following details:
• Name and profile picture  
• Bio describing my interests in programming and technology  
• Academic details (B.Tech CSE student)  

I also learned how to:
• Create repositories  
• Upload files and projects  
• Manage code using version control  

GitHub will help me in the future to showcase my coding skills and projects to recruiters and companies.

----------------------------------------

LinkedIn Profile

LinkedIn is a professional networking platform used to connect with students, professionals, and companies.

I updated my LinkedIn profile by adding:
• Full name and professional photo  
• Education details (VIT Bhopal University, B.Tech CSE)  
• Skills such as C++, problem-solving, and teamwork  
• A short summary about my career goals  

LinkedIn will help me:
• Connect with professionals  
• Explore job and internship opportunities  
• Build a strong professional network  

----------------------------------------

Importance of Digital Portfolio

Creating a digital portfolio is important because:
• It showcases skills and achievements  
• Helps in building a professional identity  
• Increases chances of getting internships and jobs  
• Allows easy sharing of work with others  

----------------------------------------

Future Plan

Over the next four years, I plan to:
• Regularly upload coding projects on GitHub  
• Improve my programming skills  
• Stay active on LinkedIn and connect with professionals  
• Build a strong and attractive digital portfolio  

----------------------------------------

Conclusion

This task helped me understand the importance of maintaining a professional online presence. Platforms like GitHub and LinkedIn play a major role in career development. By continuously updating my portfolio, I can improve my chances of success in the future.
